@startuml ecu-vmodel-lifecycle
title ECU Development V-Model Lifecycle
skinparam wrapWidth 200

left to right direction

rectangle "SYS.1\nRequirements Elicitation" as SYS1
rectangle "SYS.2\nSystem Req. Analysis" as SYS2
rectangle "SYS.3\nSystem Arch. Design" as SYS3
rectangle "SWE.1\nSW Requirements Analysis" as SWE1
rectangle "SWE.2\nSW Architectural Design" as SWE2
rectangle "SWE.3\nDetailed Design &\nUnit Construction" as SWE3
rectangle "SWE.4\nSW Unit Verification" as SWE4
rectangle "SWE.5\nSW Integration & Test" as SWE5
rectangle "SYS.4\nSystem Integration & Test" as SYS4
rectangle "SYS.5\nSystem Qualification Test" as SYS5
rectangle "SOP\n(Start of Production)" as SOP
rectangle "Field Maintenance\nSUP.9 / SUP.10" as FIELD

SYS1 --> SYS2
SYS2 --> SYS3
SYS3 --> SWE1
SWE1 --> SWE2
SWE2 --> SWE3
SWE3 --> SWE4 : implementation point\n(bottom of the V)
SWE4 --> SWE5
SWE5 --> SYS4
SYS4 --> SYS5
SYS5 --> SOP
SOP --> FIELD
FIELD ..> SYS1 : field defect / change request\nre-opens left side

note bottom of SWE3
  MCAL configuration and
  CDD code are written here.
end note

@enduml
